            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the<strong> mozzarella </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Pick your <strong>basil leaves</strong> from the stalks, discard the stalks</p>",
